metadata.name: Miner Squad Vol. 1
metadata.description: The Antminer L7 Collection (also known as Miner Squad Vol. 1) is Miner Squad DAO's genesis  NFT collection. It consists of 10,000 NFTs that are tied to mining rigs owned by the DAO using blockchain technology. They each represent tokenized miner hash power on the Ethereum blockchain and grant holders an equal share of the crypto mined by the DAO and exclusive access to the Miner Squad Metaverse.
